      </w:r>
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">A restaurant at 123 Main St. Most Drops use the restaurant's address as the default. But for a special farm dinner, the host overrides the Drop Location to &quot;Green Valley Farm, 456 Rural Rd&quot;. The Account address does not change.</w:t>
