      </w:r>
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">A fitness influencer with no fixed address. Each Drop has a different location: Monday at Chautauqua Park, Wednesday at 24 Hour Fitness, Friday at a hotel rooftop. Each Drop pulls from the Saved Venue Roster or enters a new address.</w:t>
