      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">A Consumer is an individual user of the Nigh Drops app. The UI label is &quot;Guest&quot; across all consumer-facing and host-facing surfaces. The data model and backend term is &quot;Consumer&quot; in code, database schemas, and API contracts.</w:t>
