      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">The following features are planned for future releases but are explicitly excluded from the v1 scope. Each item includes a brief description, use cases, rationale for deferral, and data model implications to ensure v1 architecture does not preclude future implementation.</w:t>
