        <w:spacing w:after="120"/>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve">Travel-time-based discovery filter. Instead of simple radius (which ignores roads, traffic, transit), Nigh Zone uses isochrone mapping to show Drops reachable within a consumer-configurable time window (5-60 minutes). More honest and practical than radius-based filtering.</w:t>
